Welcome to the Phishducation application! Our goal is to make you better at finding phishing emails, and to make that process easy!

Start by logging in or registering!




What is Phishing?

A phishing attack aims to compromise data, resulting in losses and damage to both companies and individuals. The project aims to make users aware of the ten most common phishing attributes and provide a fun way to test and improve their phishing email classification abilities.
